---
title: Chicken Tikka & Garlic Rice with Tomato Salsa & Herbed Yoghurt
description: Enjoy the mild, aromatic flavours of India in this quick meal. Tender strips of chicken get a light tandoori coating, which goes perfectly with fragrant garlic rice. A collection of zesty side dishes takes this dinner to the next level: there's a fresh salad, creamy yoghurt sauce and sweet chutney to cover all your bases.

*Each week, we search the country to source the best ingredients, with a focus on quality and variety. This week's cherry tomatoes were in short supply, so we've replaced them with gourmet tomatoes. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
